snippet.title: FFVII: Re-Imagined
snippet.description:
http://ffvii-reimagined.com/

Final Fantasy VII re-imagined as a 2D action side scroller.

All trademarks of FFVII belongs to Square Enix. This is a non-profit fan made project, done purely for fun. In no way does the fans who made the project is seeking to profit from the fan project.
